               <p>FIVE OTHER COUNTS, charging the prisoner Sandford as in the above Counts; and the prisoner Lesslie with feloniously inciting, moving, procuring, aiding, counselling, hiring, and commanding him to commit the said felony and burglary, instead of being present, aiding, abetting, and assisting.</p>
               <p>MESSRS. ADOLPHUS and CLARKSON conducted the prosecution.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18291029-189-person1518">
                  JOHN 
                  EVANS
               <interp inst="t18291029-189-person1518" type="surname" value="EVANS"></interp>
