            . I am a painter, and live in Grangecourt. I have known Lesslie eight months - he bore a very honest character, as far as I know.</p>
               <p>MR. ADOLPHUS. Q. Did you lodge in the same house with Sandford and Lesslie in Grange - court? A. Yes - Sandford lived there about seven months ago; I never heard any thing against his honesty - I know nothing of Mr. Edge.</p>
               <p>Seven other witnesses gave Lesslie a good character.</p>
               <p>SANDFORD - <rs id="t18291029-189-verdict1063" type="verdictDescription">
